                  <fr:mainmatter><html:p>For any <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000B.xml" title="precategory" addr="forest://erct/erct-000B" type="local">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex>, the type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{
